  "commentary": {
    "neutral_announcer_espn": "A lengthy dink battle unfolds at the net. Both players are demonstrating excellent touch and control, keeping the ball low and in play. The pressure builds with each exchange, and eventually, one player makes a slight miscalculation, sending the ball into the net.",
    "hype_announcer_charged": "OH MY GOODNESS! We've got a DINK-FEST going on here! These two are going toe-to-toe, trading blows like a heavyweight bout, but with the softest touch you've ever seen! The crowd is on the edge of their seats... and... NOOOO! It's in the net! What a rally, but it ends with a heartbreaking error!",
